# Sequential Variable Test

This tests whether variables are processed in document order.

<<var:a type="number">>25<</var>>
First value of a: ${a}

<<var:a>>50<</var>>
Second value of a: ${a}

<<var:name>>Alice<</var>>
Name: ${name}

<<var:name>>Bob<</var>>
Name after update: ${name}

---

If this works correctly, you should see:
- First value of a: 25
- Second value of a: 50
- Name: Alice
- Name after update: Bob
